body:
Perhaps @Signaltonsalat means that after you construct a Road object, you can add a renderPriority property into the object. For example:

road1 = Road("invisible_texture", "", true)

// Add a custom property, like renderPriority
road1.renderPriority = "10"

// Call the add road function to append this road1 
// object with custom property inside the scenario
beamngpy.add_road(road1)
